(17, 'branchreview/img/branch_info17.jpeg', 'img/branch_info_b17.jpeg', 'IIT Bhubaneshwar', 'Mechanical Engineering', '<p>Internationally acclaimed and a premier learning institute is what IIT-Bhubaneshwar is. The department believes in creating new opportunities for students in terms of academics, research and overall development.</p>', '<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Well-equipped laboratories make up infrastructure here. Following laboratories are a part of the department:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Machine &amp; Mechanism Laboratory</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Mechanical Engineering Workshop</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-CAD / CAM / CAE Laboratory</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Advanced Product Development Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Thermo-Fluids Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Fluid Dynamics Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-AI Machine-Learning &amp; Mechatronics Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Instrumentation Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Acoustics &amp; Vibrations Lab</span></p>', '<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><strong><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\"><em>Job/Placement &amp; Business Opportunities</em></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><strong><em><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Placement Overview</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Approximately 15-18 companies recruit mechanical engineers from here, out of which 3-4 companies are core. Although core companies are quite less, but non-core sector also hold immense scope.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><strong><em><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Name of Companies visiting campus for recruitment</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Following companies recruit Mechanical engineers from here:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Tata Consultancy Services (R&amp;D Division)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Deloitte (USA)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Infosys</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Flipkart Online Service</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Altair Engineering</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Avtec</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Tata Motors</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Headstrong Services India Pvt. Ltd.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-3DPLM Software Solution</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Tata Consulting Engineers</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-UnitedHealth Group</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Cognizant</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-heigh