(18, 'branchreview/img/branch_info18.jpeg', 'img/branch_info_b18.jpeg', 'IIT Bhubaneshwar', 'Electrical Engineering', '<p>The main motive is to inculcate spirit of professionalism in students who are our future leaders and whose innovative ideas might contribute to some way in this era of technology. They are also encouraged to take care of the environment as well. Hence the main motive is overall development of students.</p>', '<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Well-equipped laboratories make up infrastructure here. Following laboratories are a part of the department:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Digital Signal Processing &amp; Embedded Systems Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-VLSI Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Power &amp; Energy Systems Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Signals &amp; Networks Lab</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-seri