ont-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-HCL</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">-Affine Analytics</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1', '<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">The faculties hold the responsibility for the brighter future of students. They try and teach the students all the basics. Although the department lacks in mentorship programs.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p>Universities like University of Edinburgh, UK, University of Western Ontario, Canada and University of Texas, North Denton, USA have signed MOU with the department. &nbsp;</p>', '<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><strong><em><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Conferences/Seminars</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.0pt;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \\''Helvetica\\'',\\''sans-serif\\''; color: #555555;\\">Quite a large number of conferences and seminars are organised in the department and some are organised as a part of Wissenaire, a technical fest.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'branchreview/see_branch_review.php?id=18', 'IIT9 Bhubaneshwar Electrical Engineering EE99 '),
(19, 'branchreview/img/branch_info19.jpeg', 'img/branch_info_b19.jpeg', 'NIT Allahabad ', 'Mechanical Engineering ', '<p>The department of Mechanical Engineering is the largest and oldest department at MNNIT comprising the maximum of students NIT Allahabad Mechanical Engineering and faculty. The department is divided into four subgroups Design Engineering, Production and Industrial Engineering, Thermal Engineering and Chemical Engineering. The Department offers 3 undergraduate programs in Mechanical Engineering, Production and Industrial Engineering and Chemical Engineering with about 150 students being registered every year for these three courses. The additional feature of the department&rsquo;s faculty is that about 90% of them have doctoral degree and rest are pursuing one. What basically is the motive of the department is to offer best of education, an amalgamation of traditional and modern techniques.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Well Equipped laboratories are a necessity for any branch. Regular maintenance is being done in order to ensure latest technologies at the footsteps of students.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The department comprises of following labs:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thermal Engineering Laboratories</li>\r\n<li>Production and Industrial Engineering Laboratories</li>\r\n<li>Design Engineering Labs</li>\r\n<li>Mechanical Engineering Workshop </li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Placement Overview</strong></p>\r\n<p>With the sudden boom in technology companies want individuals who have knowledge in accordance with modern technology.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Some of the companies that visit MNNIT for Mechanical branch are listed below:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>HPCL-Mittal Energy Ltd. (HMEL)</li>\r\n<li>BPCL</li>\r\n<li>Afcons Infrastructure Ltd.</li>\r\n<li>Parker Hennifin India</li>\r\n<li>ReInspire Tech</li>\r\n<li>Schaeffler India</li>\r\n<li>Binani Cements</li>\r\n<li>TAFE</li>\r\n<li>FIAT India Automative Ltd</li>\r\n<li>Raymond Engineering</li>\r\n<li>JSW Steel Ltd</li>\r\n<li>Reliance industries ltd.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Average Package: </strong>5.7 LPA</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Package:</strong> 14 LPA</p>\r\n<p><strong>Percentage Placement:</strong> Out of 92 eligible students 79 were placed.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Branch Scenario:</strong></p>\r\n<p><em>Further Studies/Research Scope:</em></p>\r\n<p>If one wants to pursue further studies loads of doors are open like Mtech, MBA and IAS with each field having its own pros and cons.Course Curriculum are upgraded as per new technology</p>\r\n<p>With evolving technology in machines course upgradation is done on a regular basis. </p>', '<p>The department comprises of 11 professors, 5 associate professors, 21 assistant professors having deep knowledge of the subject and have carried out research in the following fields:<br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fatigue &amp; Fracture&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Computer Aided Design (CAD)</li>\r\n<li>Computer Integrated Manufacturing (CIM)</li>\r\n<li>Supply Chain Management</li>\r\n<li>Advanced Manufacturing Processes</li>\r\n<li>Laser Material Processing</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>With Universities (Indian/Foreign): The department aims at collaborating with various foreign universities to offer the best of knowledge to students.</p>', '<p><strong>Conferences/Seminars:</strong></p>\r\n<p>A large number of conferences are organized to encourage the students to do research in various fields and help them strengthen their concepts.</p>', 'branchreview/see_branch_review.php?id=19', 'NIT9 Allahabad Mech Mechanical Engineering '),
