(24, '<b>2015 Top Placement<br></b>1.83 Cr by Oracle<br><br><b>Top Recruiters<br></b>Google, Microsoft,<br>Oracle etc<b><br></b>', 'Nearest Airport :Jolly Grant Airport(64 Km)<br><br>Nearest Railway Station : Roorkee Railway Station(3-4 Km)<br><br>&nbsp; Nearest Bus Depot: Roorkee Bus Depot, NH58<br>', 'IIT Roorkee', 'Indian Institute of Technology Roorkee (commonly known as IIT Roorkee or IITR), formerly the University of Roorkee (19482001) and the Thomason College of Civil Engineering (18531948), is a public university located in Roorkee, Uttarakhand, India. Established in 1847, was converted into an Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) in 2001, thus becoming the seventh IIT to be declared.<br>IIT Roorkee has 18 academic departments covering Engineering, Applied Sciences, Humanities &amp; Social Scien', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/Co4CGjYwHF4', 'http://www.iitr.ac.in/', 'IIT Roorkee Campus, Haridwar Highway, Roorkee, Uttarakhand 247667', 'regis@iitr.ernet.in', '01332 285 311', '365 acres (1,480,000 m2)', 'Air Conditioned Classrooms, Top Notch Sports Facilities, World Class Library, LAN and Wifi Facilities', 'It is a two step process.<br>First a candidate needs <br>to appear in JEE Mains and<br>&nbsp;then in JEE Advanced.<br>', ' 77880 INR', '10,500', 'http://www.iitr.ac.in/academics/uploads/File/2015/fee%20structure/UG%20fee%20structure.pdf', '../../engcolleges/php/pics/a24.jpeg', '../../engcolleges/php/pics/b24.jpeg', '../../engcolleges/php/pics/c24.jpeg', '../../engcolleges/php/pics/d24.jpeg', '../../engcolleges/php/pics/e24.jpeg', 'Chemical Engineering,Civil Engineering,Computer Science and Engineering,Electrical Engineering,Electronics and Communication Engineering,Engineering Physics,Mechanical Engineering,Metallurgical and Materials Engineering,Polymer Science and Engineering,roduction and Industrial Engineering', 'Architecture', 'Geological Technology,Geophysical Technology', 'Applied Mathematics', 'Biotechnology,18,7.6', 'Adobe Systems India Pvt. Ltd.,AIR Worldwide India Pvt. Ltd.,Amazon Development Centre (India) Pvt. Ltd.,Airbus Engineering Centre India,Bank of India,BROADCOM INDIA PVT LTD,Flipkart', 'Amazon,Google,Oracle,Microsoft', '../../engcolleges/php/pics/co24.jpeg', 'engcolleges/php/pics/i24.jpeg', 'engcolleges/php/see_college.php?id=24', 'IIT9 Roorkee IITR'),
