(101, 'UPSEE 2016 Counselling Dates Announced', '<p>Uttar Pradesh Technical University (UPTU) has released the counselling schedule for UPSEE 2016 on its official website. The counselling process begins from June 24, 2016 and the same will get closed on August 5. UPSEE 2016 was conducted on April 17, 23, and 24, 2016 at different centres in India. It is conducted by UPTU for admissions to various B.Tech programmes, offered by different colleges in Uttar Pradesh.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>UPSEE 2016 counselling will be conducted by Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam Technical University (AKTU) in four different rounds and each round will be held in different time slot. To take a look at the detailed counselling process for UPSEE 2016, <a href="../../news/php/article.php?id=100" target="_blank">click here</a>!</p>\r\n<p>The schedule of all the four round counselling is mentioned below, candidates who appeared for the exam can check for the details:</p>\r\n<table class="MsoTableGrid" style="border: none;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 233.75pt; border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; background: #f4b083;" valign="top" width="312">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;">DATE</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 233.75pt; border-top-width: 1pt; border-right-width: 1pt; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-style: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt; background: #f4b083;" valign="top" width="312">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;">EVENT</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 233.75pt; border-right-width: 1pt; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-left-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top-style: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt;" valign="top" width="312">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;">