(104, 'IEC University announces B.Tech admissions 2016', '<p>IEC University has announced B.Tech admissions for 2016-17 session. For admission to the University, candidates are required to fill the application form in online mode only till August 15, 2016. It is must for every candidate to appear and qualify either in JEE Main 2016 or in HPCET 2016 for admission to IEC University. At the time of admission to the University, candidates are also required to submit the below listed documents as proof of their age, 10+2 marks and entrance exam qualification. Candidates aspiring for admission to the University can check all the details related to IEC University B.Tech admissions 2016 below on this page.<br /><br /><strong>Eligibility Criteria:</strong><br />All aspirants must have passed their 10+2 or equivalent examination from a recognized board/University with a minimum of 50% marks.<br />All aspiring candidates must have studied Mathematics &amp; Physics as compulsory subjects and any of the subjects out of Chemistry/Computer Science/Biochemistry/Biology/Technical Vocation Subjects<br /><strong><br />Application Form:</strong><br /> <br /><strong>Online:</strong> Application forms can be filled in online mode only by the candidates aspiring for admission to IEC University. While filling the application forms, candidates are required to fill their personal details, qualification details, category and state domicile. After filling all the details, candidates are required to click on &ldquo;Submit&rdquo; button for submission of application form. To fill the application form, candidates can click on the link given below.<br /><br /><strong><em><a href="http://www.iecuniversity.com/homes/online-admission" target="_blank">Click here</a> to fill the application form of IEC University<br /><br /></em>Documents required at the time of Admission:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p a